            <description sparkle:format="plain-text">
- NEW: Right-click on the dock icon to show the list of commands.
- NEW: Now you can drop an image onto the dock icon then ask questions about it.
- CHANGED: The quick command window is now the main window. Use the menu bar to create a stand-alone window if needed.
- FIXED: The response is not visible if it is too short.
            </description>
